commit.message:
Remove now redundant manual cleanup-modules directive.

2012-05-15  Bernhard Reutner-Fischer  <aldot@gcc.gnu.org>

	* gfortran.dg/*.f90: Remove now redundant manual
	cleanup-modules directive.

From-SVN: r187521
